Set up your work environment (cont.)

/etc/mk.conf

There are some important variables which everyone who's working with the ports tree should use:

SUDO=/usr/bin/sudo
PLIST_DB=${PORTSDIR}/plist
WRKOBJDIR=/usr/obj/ports
USE_SYSTRACE=Yes


